Subject: [PATCH] blk-rq-qos: fix crash on rq_qos_wait vs. rq_qos_wake_function
 race

commit e972b08b91ef48488bae9789f03cfedb148667fb upstream.

We're seeing crashes from rq_qos_wake_function that look like this:

